{
  "texts": [
    "The method first extracts discriminative features from the deep CNN for shot segmentation.",
    "Then, memory features and entropy features of the image are predicted from the CNN model.",
    "The extracted features are efficiently computed by a hierarchical weighted fusion mechanism to generate an aggregation score.",
    "Finally, the aggregation score is used to compose an attention curve to locate salient keyframes.",
    "The effectiveness of the framework is finally validated experimentally."
  ]
}